    <table width="100%">
		<tr>
			<td width="60%" style="vertical-align:top;">
				 <div class="lost message" >
			      <h3>Review and approval requirements:</h3>
				  <ul>
				  <li >Legal review is required anytime a contract must be approved by PS CEO or EC, or if the template is not an <b><u>unmodified</u></b> Danfoss Approved Template.</li>
				  <li>PS CEO approval is required if the contact amount is 15M - 17M, depending on the contract type.</li>
				  <li>EC approval is required if the contract amount is greater than 17M, depending on the contract type; or if the contract duration is greater than 3 years without a cancellation clause, the customer is a competitor, the application is high risk or the market is dominated by Danfoss Group.</li>
				  </ul>
			    </div>	
			</td>
			<td width="40%" style="vertical-align:top;">
				 <div class="lost message" >
