				  <ul>
				  <li>Contract must be reviewed with Legal if the Legal Review Required field has a green checkmark</li>
				  <li>Business Impact must be reviewed</li>
				  <li>Contract type and template must match the contract content</li>
				  </ul>
			    </div>	
			</td>
		</tr>
	</table>
   
